{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I’m working a lot with motion and animation,"},{"time":4000,"text":"and also I'm an old DJ and a musician."},{"time":9000,"text":"So, music videos are something that I always found interesting,"},{"time":14000,"text":"but they always seem to be so reactive."},{"time":16000,"text":"So I was thinking, can you remove us as creators"},{"time":23000,"text":"and try to make the music be the voice"},{"time":27000,"text":"and have the animation following it?"},{"time":30000,"text":"So with two designers, Tolga and Christina, at my office, we took a track --"},{"time":38000,"text":"many of you probably know it. It’s about 25 years old,"},{"time":41000,"text":"and it's David Byrne and Brian Eno --"},{"time":44000,"text":"and we did this little animation."},{"time":47000,"text":"And I think that it's maybe interesting, also,"},{"time":50000,"text":"that it deals with two problematic issues,"},{"time":53000,"text":"which are rising waters and religion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"Song: Before God destroyed the people on the Earth,"},{"time":79000,"text":"he warned Noah to build an Ark."},{"time":85000,"text":"And after Noah built his Ark,"},{"time":89000,"text":"I believe he told Noah to warn the people"},{"time":95000,"text":"that they must change all their wicked ways"},{"time":99000,"text":"before he come upon them and destroy them."},{"time":105000,"text":"And when Noah had done built his Ark,"},{"time":109000,"text":"I understand that somebody began to rend a song."},{"time":118000,"text":"And the song began to move on I understand like this."},{"time":131000,"text":"And when Noah had done built his Ark ..."},{"time":142000,"text":"Move on ... In fact ... Concern ..."},{"time":162000,"text":"So they get tired, has come dark and rain; they get weary and tired."},{"time":172000,"text":"And then he went and knocked an old lady house."},{"time":174000,"text":"And old lady ran to the door and say, \"Who is it?\""},{"time":181000,"text":"Jack say, \"Me, Mama-san, could we spend the night here?"},{"time":184000,"text":"Because we’re far from home, we’re very tired.\""},{"time":192000,"text":"And the old lady said, \"Oh yes, come on in.\""},{"time":201000,"text":"It was come dark and rain, will make you weary and tired."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}